name: Duwendeng Itim
description: Duwendeng Itim (Black Dwarves) are tiny, malevolent forest spirits. They are easily offended and are known to kidnap the children of the offending human as punishment for their perceived slights. They lure their young victims by promising to give them their hearts desire. Once the child agrees, they become forever trapped inside the underground domicile of the vengeful Duwendeng Itim.
